description:
7 Day Free Trial of Pimsleur - https://imp.i271380.net/YgN9kJ

I highly recommend that you give Pimsleur a try for free for 7 days, as it has transformed the way I study Russian and Arabic. Basically you listen to 30 minute lessons where you start speaking the language from Day 1 by repeating important sentences out loud, and it is INSANELY EFFECTIVE. I decided to learn Modern Standard Arabic on it, and I was having a blast making good progress within my first 30 minute lesson. I was seriously speaking better Modern Standard Arabic than Egyptian after a few days of Pimsleur even though I spent a few months self studying Egyptian. Then I also use it to improve my Russian, as the audio only nature of it allows me to not hurt my eyes given my eye problem. You don't really have anything to lose if you try it for 7 days, just remember to cancel if you decide it's not for you. Also, you will be supporting my channel if you give it a try!

Join my Patreon to learn how I study languages - https://www.patreon.com/languagesimp

Check out my Merch including the shirt I wear in this vid!  - https://language-simp-store.creator-spring.com/
